WEBVTT

00:02.733 --> 00:03.343
Bare.

00:04.133 --> 00:05.755
He walked in bare feet.

00:07.167 --> 00:09.411
He walked on the road in bare feet.

00:10.854 --> 00:11.319
Care.

00:12.132 --> 00:13.491
Please take care of her.

00:14.876 --> 00:16.573
Please take good care of her.

00:17.845 --> 00:18.439
Fare.

00:19.165 --> 00:20.830
The train fare was cheap.

00:22.219 --> 00:24.121
The train fare was quite cheap.

00:25.522 --> 00:26.019
Hare.

00:26.831 --> 00:28.335
The hare ran away.

00:29.725 --> 00:32.141
The hare ran away into the forest.

00:37.603 --> 00:40.832
Deserts are very, very dry and hot.

00:41.353 --> 00:44.138
Ocean water is very, very salty.

00:45.115 --> 00:48.316
Mountains are very, very tall and steep.

00:48.831 --> 00:52.071
Plains are very, very grassy and flat.

00:52.587 --> 00:55.845
Rainforests are very, very wet.

00:56.111 --> 00:58.827
The tundra is very, very cold.

01:00.061 --> 01:03.511
Plants and animals live all around the world.

01:03.818 --> 01:06.663
Deserts, oceans, mountains!

01:07.573 --> 01:10.149
Plains, rainforests, tundra!

